						<div class="postbody">Tepples's suggestion (just have the DAC output a constant value of 7.5 when ultrasonic) is actually what correct antialiasing would result in, so I'm not certain it's actually a hack. Especially if you keep the phase running for whenever the game brings the pitch back down to audible frequencies.</div>

